entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You succeeded in defeating the Chirq Council by destroying their leadership, the Elite Council.
entries.journal_entry_description: The Chirq Council is lead by nine members known as the Elite Council. If the Elite Council were destroyed, it is highly possible that the Chirq Council will collapse.
entries.journal_entry_title: The Chirq Council: The Elite Council
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: The Elite Council members are housed in two bunkers.
entries.task01_entrance_waypoint_name: Entrance to the First Elite Council Bunker
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: The first bunker is home to four of the Elite Council members. Terminate them.
entries.task01_journal_entry_title: The First Four Elite Council Members
entries.task01_waypoint_name: Entrance to the First Elite Council Bunker
entries.task02_entrance_waypoint_name: Entrance to the Second Elite Council Bunker
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: The final five members of the Elite Council are in the second bunker. Terminate them.
entries.task02_journal_entry_title: The Last Five Elite Council Members
entries.task02_waypoint_name: Entrance to the Second Elite Council Bunker
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Report to Captain Baize and let her know that you've defeated the Elite Council. The Chirq Council should be in chaos if not utterly destroyed.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Terminate Zuld Mar-Shayal of the Elite Council.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Terminate Janos Zarbo of the Elite Council.
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: Terminate Braganti Hooge of the Elite Council.
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: Terminate Markus Gilder of the Elite Council.
entries.task08_journal_entry_description: Terminate Koran Lassk of the Elite Council.
entries.task09_journal_entry_description: Terminate Atlan Dubreas of the Elite Council.
entries.task10_journal_entry_description: Terminate Crale Forte of the Elite Council.
entries.task11_journal_entry_description: Terminate Mathazar Zayet of the Elite Council.
entries.task12_journal_entry_description: Terminate Rallyn Secura of the Elite Council.
